{%- assign conda = include.conda %}
{%- assign cinstall = conda.install | default: page.packages %}
**Load module `miniconda`** to access Conda commands to create environments, activate them, and install packages.
    ```
    module load miniconda
    conda create --name {{ conda.env }}
    source activate {{ conda.env }}
    conda install{% if cinstall.first %}{% for _c in cinstall %} {{ _c }}{% endfor %}{% else %} {{ cinstall }}{% endif %}
    ```